{"title":"while循环","date":"2019-08-16T14:46:15.000Z","link":"post/while循环","tags":["while循环"],"categories":["python"],"updated":"2019-08-16T16:06:17.023Z","content":"<h2 id=\"while循环格式\">while循环格式<a href=\"post/while循环#while循环格式\"></a></h2><p>while 条件或语句 ：</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">current_number = <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> current_number &lt;=<span class=\"number\">5</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(current_number)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    current_number += <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"while退出循环方式\">while退出循环方式<a href=\"post/while循环#while退出循环方式\"></a></h2><h4 id=\"判断条件退出\">判断条件退出<a href=\"post/while循环#判断条件退出\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>数字可用==  &lt;=  &gt;= !=判断退出</li>\n<li>字符可用==  !=判断退出</li>\n<li>列表或字典转移或清空时，可用变量名判断退出，元素为空时，默认False退出。</li>\n<li>当需要清除列表或字典中某个元素时，emmm，看实例吧，说不清哈哈哈<del>~</del></li>\n<li>设置变量为True，在循环体内判断，更改为False为退出</li>\n<li>break方法适用所有循环退出，结合if语句即可</li>\n<li>当需要持续循环时，运用True进行循环</li>\n<li>注意：True与False均为首字母大写</li>\n</ol>\n<p>实例1：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">current_number = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> current_number &lt; <span class=\"number\">10</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    current_number += <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> current_number % <span class=\"number\">2</span> == <span class=\"number\">0</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">continue</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(current_number)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>实例2：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">message = <span class=\"string\">\"\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> message != <span class=\"string\">\"quit\"</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    message = input()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(message)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>实例3：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">unconfirmed_users = [&apos;alice&apos;, &apos;vrian&apos;, &apos;candace&apos;]</span><br><span class=\"line\">confirmed_users = []</span><br><span class=\"line\">while unconfirmed_users:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    current_user = unconfirmed_users.pop()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(&quot;Verifying user: &quot; + current_user.title())</span><br><span class=\"line\">    confirmed_users.append(current_user)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(&quot;\\nThe following users have been confirmed:&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">for confirmed_user in confirmed_users:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(confirmed_user.title())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>实例4：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pets = [<span class=\"string\">'dog'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'cat'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'dog'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'goldfish'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'cat'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'rabbbit'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'cat'</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(pets)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"string\">'cat'</span> <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> pets:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    pets.remove(<span class=\"string\">'cat'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(pets)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>实例5：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">responses = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">polling_active = True</span><br><span class=\"line\">while polling_active:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    name = input(&quot;\\nwhat is your name?&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    response = input(&quot;which mountain would you like to climb someday? &quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    responses[name] = response</span><br><span class=\"line\">    repeat = input(&quot;would you like to let another person respond? (yes/no)&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if repeat == &apos;no&apos;:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        polling_active = False</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(&quot;\\n---Poll Results---&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">for name,response in responses.items():</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(name + &quot; would like to climb &quot; + response + &quot;.&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>实例6&amp;7：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">while True:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    city = input()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if city == &apos;quit&apos;:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        break</span><br><span class=\"line\">    else:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(&quot;I&apos;d love to go to &quot; + city.title() + &quot;!&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"continue语句\">continue语句<a href=\"post/while循环#continue语句\"></a></h2><p>continue通常结合if语句使用，执行结果为跳过continue后循环体内语句</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">current_number = 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">while current_number &lt; 10:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    current_number += 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if current_number % 2 == 0:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        continue</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(current_number)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","next":{"title":"输入","link":"post/输入"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/post/while循环/","toc":[{"title":"while循环格式","id":"while循环格式","index":"1"},{"title":"while退出循环方式","id":"while退出循环方式","index":"2"},{"title":"continue语句","id":"continue语句","index":"3"}]}